{{NBA獎項}}
'''NBA終身成就獎'''（{{lang-en|NBA Lifetime Achievement Award}}）是於2017年設立的[[NBA|NBA]]年度獎項，頒發給有極大貢獻的NBA球員。首年得獎者為[[標·羅素|標·羅素]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nba.com/article/2017/06/15/bill-russell-receive-lifetime-achievement-award-nba-awards-2017|title=Bill Russell to receive Lifetime Achievement Award at NBA Awards|publisher=[[NBA|NBA]]|date=2017-06-15|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728181859/https://www.nba.com/article/2017/06/15/bill-russell-receive-lifetime-achievement-award-nba-awards-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

